dct_title_s: A new map of Turkey in Asia
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Shows Cyprus and part of Europe. Prime meridian: London. "Printed ... as the Act directs Jany. 6th. 1789." Probably issued in: A general atlas, describing the whole universe ... : the whole being an improvement of the maps of D'Anville and Robert / engraved in the best manner on sixty-two copper-plates, by Thomas Kitchin, senior, and others ... London : Printed for Robert Sayer, no. 53, Fleet-street, [1790?]
